+if $tracelevel then {
+    strace $tracelevel
+}
+
+# load support procs
+load_lib objc-torture.exp
+
+#
+# main test loop
+#
+
+foreach src [lsort [glob -nocomplain $srcdir/$subdir/*.m]] {
+    # If we're only testing specific files and this isn't one of them, skip it.
+    if ![runtest_file_p $runtests $src] then {
+	continue
+    }
+
+    objc-torture $src
+}
